<h1>Question:</h1>
<p> A house has four walls. All of the walls are facing south, and a bear is circling the house. What color is the bear?</p>
<ol> 
    <li> Red
    <li> Blue
        <li> Green
            <ol/>
    
<h2>Answer:</h2>
<p>The house is on the north pole, so the circling bear is white.</p>
